        ("TDS Rules", "What is the TDS Rules page?",
            "Go to TDS Rules in the sidebar. It shows a Live Calculator (enter section, amount, deductee type → get TDS instantly), a full Rate Table for all sections under the current FY, and a Due Dates reference. Useful for quick lookups without leaving the app."),
        ("TDS Rules", "How do I calculate TDS for a specific section quickly?",
            "Go to TDS Rules → Live Calculator tab. Select section, enter amount, select deductee type (Individual / Company / etc.), tick PAN Available if applicable. CDeTDS shows TDS amount, effective rate and applicable rule instantly."),
        ("TDS Rules", "What happened to Section 206AB from FY 2025-26?",
            "Section 206AB (higher TDS for ITR non-filers) was removed by Finance Act 2025 with effect from 1-Apr-2025. From FY 2025-26 onwards, the higher-rate provision no longer applies. The checkbox in TDS Rules is shown but disabled to reflect this."),

