        ("Audit Log", "What is the Audit Log?",
            "Every action in CDeTDS (login, add/edit/delete deductee, generate FVU, settings change, etc.) is logged with username, timestamp and details. Go to Audit Log in the sidebar to review. You can filter by user, module, date range and search keywords."),
        ("Audit Log", "How do I export the Audit Log?",
            "Go to Audit Log → click Export CSV (top-right). The full filtered log is saved as a CSV file. Useful for compliance reviews or sharing with auditors."),

