        ("Excel Import", "What can I import from Excel?",
            "Go to Excel Import/Export → Import Data tab. You can bulk-import: TDS Entries, Deductee Master, Challans (ITNS 281), Employee Master (for 24Q payroll), and TRACES Conso File. Download the sample template first, fill it, then upload."),
        ("Excel Import", "How do I export data to Excel or Tally?",
